Hindi kailangang magmadali.

00:12:57.648 --> 00:12:58.582
Nagmamadali ako.

00:13:00.351 --> 00:13:02.653
Baka hindi ko
na maibalik sa dati ang paa ko.

00:13:02.720 --> 00:13:04.421
Hindi mangyayari 'yan.

00:13:04.955 --> 00:13:05.923
Sumasakay ka, 'di ba?

00:13:05.990 --> 00:13:07.625
Hindi sapat na sakyan lang ito.

00:13:08.726 --> 00:13:10.728
Wala namang saysay kung hindi tayo mananalo, 'di ba?

00:13:12.129 --> 00:13:13.430
Simula nang bumalik ako,

00:13:14.265 --> 00:13:16.734
Hindi pa ako nakapaglagay kahit isang beses.

00:13:18.168 --> 00:13:19.236
Shohei...

00:13:21.906 --> 00:13:22.940
Pasensya na.

